## User activation cheat sheet (copy to Cursor User Rules if desired)

**This rule is `alwaysApply: true` — you do not need to re-explain topology or Guía.**

| Goal | Say |
|------|-----|
| New slim plan | `Haz un plan para <tarea>` |
| Prompts to run it | `Dame los prompts del plan <slug>` or `Guía + prompt 3` |
| Next step | `<SA> terminó OK — siguiente prompt` |
| Run one step in this chat | Paste one `text` block only |
| No subagents | `solo en este chat` |

**Opt-in full prompts inside plan file:** only if user says `incluye prompts en el plan`.
